                "incident_source": [
                  "POLIS"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "A beam of 12.3 MeV purely vector polarized",
                "deuterons initiated (d,p) reactions in targets placed",
                "in the main scattering chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SIBAR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "Four silicon surface-barrier detector telescopes"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The oxygen target was a 1.3 mg/cm2 thick foil of",
                "cellulose acetate (C7H16O9), and the magnesium target",
                "consisted of a 4 mg/cm2 metallic strip enriched to",
                "99.7% 24Mg."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "MONITOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "1",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "2-HE-4(D,EL)2-HE-4,,DA",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "2-HE-4(D,EL)2-HE-4,,DA",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "2-HE-4(D,EL)2-HE-4",
                        "target": "2-HE-4",
                        "projectile": "D",
                        "process": "EL",
                        "product": "2-HE-4",
                        "quantity": ",DA",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",DA"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The polarimeter was cross",
                "calibrated against the VAP at 45 degr.(lab),which",
                "was taken to be 0.38 for 8.96 MeV mid-target energy.",
                "The gas polarimeter containned 2.2 mg/cm2 of helium.",
                "The scattered deuterons were detected at 45 degr.",
                "with +-1 degr. extreme angular acceptances.The",
                "additional uncertainty on the VAP of the reaction which",
                "is believed to be +-3%."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "2",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": null,
                "reaction": {
                  "code": "6-C-12(D,P)6-C-13,,POL/DA",
                  "code_unit": [
                    {
                      "unit": "6-C-12(D,P)6-C-13,,POL/DA",
                      "field": {
                        "reaction": "6-C-12(D,P)6-C-13",
                        "target": "6-C-12",
                        "projectile": "D",
                        "process": "P",
                        "product": "6-C-13",
                        "quantity": ",POL/DA",
                        "data_type": null,
                        "general_quantity_modifier": null,
                        "quantity_236": ",POL/DA"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                "The beam polarization was",
                "measured by a polarimeter employing the reaction.The",
                "polarimeter consisted of a 7 mm wide strip of 12.5 mg/c",
                "thick polyethylene,viewed by silicon detectors at +-57",
                "degr.(lab) with extreme angular acceptances of +-9 degr",
                "The asymmetries in these polarimeters were in both case",
                "related to the VAP of the reaction at 60 degr.(lab)",
                "measured simultaneously in the main chamber with a",
                "5.5 mg/cm2 polyethylene target."
              ]
            }
          ],
